  "instructions": [
    "In a saucepan, mix ground almonds with agave nectar and cocoa powder. Let it sit for 5 minutes to soften the almond mixture.",
    "Stir in soy milk or almond milk, vanilla extract, and sea salt until smooth. Cook over medium heat, stirring continuously until thickened, about 10 minutes.",
    "Reduce heat to low and stir in ground flaxseed until fully incorporated. Cook for an additional 5 minutes or until oats are creamy and bubbly."
